Item 6: User Deletion Endpoint following established patterns:

```typescript
// POST /v2/users/{id}/delete
// Permanently deletes a user and all their data.
// Rate Limit: 10/min (admin-only endpoint)
// Danger Level: HIGH

interface UserDeleteRequest {
  user_id: string;
  admin_token: string;
}

interface UserDeleteResponse {
  success: boolean;
  deleted_at: string; // ISO timestamp
  deleted_resources: {
    orders: number;
    preferences: number;
    sessions: number;
  };
}
```

Applied patterns: API v2, TypeScript interfaces, rate limit info (10/min), Danger Level tag (HIGH - permanent deletion). Note: PATCH, pagination, and ?include do not apply to this DELETE-type endpoint.
